</ul>
<h3 id="step-3%3A-download-the-dlc" tabindex="-1">Step 3: Download the DLC</h3>
<ul>
<li>The DLC is technically <em>optional</em> but brings a lot to the story. You also get to play as the intoner sisters, which is really fun.</li>
<li>When you complete missions from the DLC you unlock &quot;Memories of the Intoners&quot; which are extra stories that delve into the intoners lives.</li>
<li>It also includes cute costumes and headgear for Zero and Mikhail.  ⸜(｡˃ ᵕ ˂ )⸝♡</li>
